<TEXT>
<P>
 David Letterman still hasn't lost in the ratings to Jay Leno, but Leno 
continues to close the gap. Last week his "Tonight Show" on NBC was only 
one-tenth of a point behind Letterman's "Late Show" on CBS. 
</P>
<P>
 "This marks the closest competitive position between the two shows ever with 
original telecasts," NBC said Thursday. 
