<TEXT>
<P>
 Anthony Carter scored 31 points to lead Saddleback to a 78-68 victory over 
Chaffey, the top-ranked team in the state, Thursday in the first round of the 
Fullerton men's basketball tournament. 
</P>
<P>
 Carter made all 10 of his free throws. Former Edison High standout Micah 
Kroeger had 22 points for the Gauchos. 
</P>
<P>
 Robin Kennedy had 24 points for Chaffey. 
</P>
