on varsity." He will have four returning players in the mix--one of them, Sand, 
is an all-league performer. Troy loves to shoot from outside; the Warriors hope 
to make the three-point shot a weapon, and will do it from a spread-offense 
formation that is designed to negate their smaller size and take advantage of 
their speed. "We can go inside, but there we have to be patient," Hardeman 
said. Still, Hardeman said, defense will ultimately determine the Warriors' 
standing. That, and finding a way to beat Sonora again SCHEDULE 
