<DOCNO> LA111894-0115 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 099775 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 18, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
