COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: CYPRESS; CHURCH TO DISPENSE FOOD TO THE NEEDY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BILL BILLITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Grace Church will be distributing food to needy families in the Cypress area 
Saturday and again on Dec. 17. 
</P>
<P>
 Boxes of food will be available at the church, at 5100 Cerritos Ave., from 10 
a.m. to noon each day. 
</P>
<P>
 Church officials said that more canned and bottled goods, including baby food, 
are needed, and donors may deliver the items to the church between 8 and 10 
a.m. Saturday and Dec. 17. 
</P>
