southbound San Diego Freeway. He was described as white, 25 to 30 years old, 
with heavy mustache and eyeglasses, about 6 feet tall and of medium build. 
Anyone with information regarding the incident is asked to notify the Fountain 
Valley Police Department at (714) 965-4481. 
