<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111894-0310 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 099972 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 18, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
