<TEXT>
<P>
 Proposition 187: The biographic information about Gus Frias in his Nov. 10 
commentary should have stated that he is an independent contractor, and not an 
employee, of the Los Angeles County Office of Education, and that the article 
reflected his personal opinion, not the position of the Office of Education or 
the Los Angeles County Board of Education. 
